HEADWORD: Revertive
<hw>Re*vert"ive</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Reverting, or
tending to revert; returning.</def> --
<wordforms><wf>Re*vert"ive*ly</wf>, <pos>adv.</pos></wordforms>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>The tide <qex>revertive</qex>, unattracted, leaves⟦br⟧
A yellow waste of idle sands behind.</q>
<rj><qau>Thomson.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

